===卡加利===
[[File:FairchildRadioCalgary.jpg|140px]]

{{further|加拿大中文電台FM94.7}}

加拿大中文電台的卡加利分台以FM94.7頻率播放，呼號為{{tsl|en|CHKF-FM|}}，於1998年11月啓播。<ref>{{cite web | title = Canadian Communications Foundation: CHKF-FM | publisher = Canadian Communications Foundation | date = 2004年 | url = http://www.broadcasting-history.ca/listings_and_histories/radio/histories.php?id=779&historyID=360 | accessdate = 2009-01-07 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20110611032636/http://www.broadcasting-history.ca/listings_and_histories/radio/histories.php?id=779&historyID=360 | archivedate = 2011-06-11 }}</ref>

它主要以广东话和普通话广播，也有日语，旁遮普语，印地语，西班牙语，埃塞俄比亚语，匈牙利语，波兰语等语言的节目。

